title: Legends Never Die
itunes:title: Legends Never Die
description:
Today on the show, it was only right to dedicate this episode to the Legend Kobe Bryant who tragic lost his life along with his 13 year old daughter and 7 other passengers that were on the jet. We opened up the phone lines, for listeners to send their condolences as well as deciding if they would want to know when it is there time to go!
